<plot>Sheriff "Emmy" Ellis is as dusty and desolate as the Mexican/American border she patrols -- until she recognizes a miracle -- 3 illegal women suddenly become 3 illegal mothers through a divine intervention. The chaos creates a bond between Emmy and the newborns as she realizes the mystery -- the spirits of those who died, while attempting to cross the glorious Rio Grande, are returning through women who come in contact with its waters; and with menopause on her heels, Emmy decides to create a family of her own.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?328338</url></doc>
